liblo perl binding
==================

Perl binding for the liblo library.

Only Client support is currently implemented.
See LibLO::Client for details.



INSTALLATION
------------

	I use Module::Build to build and install the module.
	To install this module type the following:
	
		perl Build.PL
		./Build
		./Build test
		
	And then as root:
	
		./Build install


